      <div class="box left">
<h3>A quick tour</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://pablonoel.com/work/">My Work</a></li>
<li><a href="https://pablonoel.com/resume/">My Resume</a></li>
<li><a href="https://pablonoel.com/articles/">My Articles</a></li>
<li><a href="https://pablonoel.com/analog/">My Passion</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="box right">
<p>I’m a Product Designer and Frontend Engineer focused on creating amazing products and services.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve held a variety of design roles since the late 1990s. I studied Biotechnology, Engineering and Communications but my love for Design was always greater.</p>
<p>I&#8217;m a passionate photographer who loves to understand and repair old cameras. I&#8217;m a devotee of medium format. With some friends we have a <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@somosbuenasuerte" target="_blank" rel="noopener">podcast where we talk about analog photography.</a></p>
</div>
<div class="box full">
<ul class='gallery'>
		<li>
			<figure><img decoding="async" src="https://pablonoel.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/MG_8856.jpg" alt="_MG_8856" /></figure>
		</li>
		<li>
